= SDL_HINT_RPI_VIDEO_LAYER =
A hint that specifies which Dispmanx layer SDL should use on a Raspberry PI.




== Values ==
{|
|X
|the Dispmanx layer to use
|}


== Default ==
By default the Dispmanx layer is "10000".


